OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773241885
OL,3,C13-year-old arrested in Sheffield over
OL,4,Csocial media posts
OL,6,FA 13-year-old boy has been arrested in
OL,7,FSheffield in connection with posts
OL,8,Fmade on social media encouraging
OL,9,Fschool children to engage in violent
OL,10,Fbehaviour.
OL,12,FThe boy remains in custody after South
OL,13,FYorkshire Police officers arrested him
OL,14,Fon suspicion of malicious
OL,15,Fcommunications, encouraging or
OL,16,Fassisting crime, and an alleged public
OL,17,Forder offence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
