OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773241885
OL,3,C13-year-old arrested in Sheffield over
OL,4,Csocial media posts
OL,6,FIt comes after South Yorkshire Police
OL,7,Fconfirmed it had been monitoring
OL,8,Fsocial media as posts linked to "red v
OL,9,Fblue school wars", a national online
OL,10,Ftrend, across the region.
OL,12,FOnline posts dividing an area's
OL,13,Fschools into blue and red teams, then
OL,14,Ftelling them to meet and fight for
OL,15,F"points", has spread across the UK.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773241885
OL,3,C13-year-old arrested in Sheffield over
OL,4,Csocial media posts
OL,6,FInsp Katie Hammond said: "We know how
OL,7,Fworried parents, families, staff and
OL,8,Fpupils have been since these social
OL,9,Fmedia posts started appearing here in
OL,10,FSouth Yorkshire and we have provided
OL,11,Fsupport and reassurance to our local
OL,12,Fschools and communities through a high-
OL,13,Fvisibility presence and increased
OL,14,Fpatrols.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773241885
OL,3,C13-year-old arrested in Sheffield over
OL,4,Csocial media posts
OL,6,F"Behind the scenes we have also been
OL,7,Factively monitoring social media and
OL,8,Fcarrying out intelligence checks, and
OL,9,Fdoing all we can to track down the
OL,10,Faccounts responsible and shut them
OL,11,Fdown. We are taking this matter
OL,12,Fseriously and are doing everything in
OL,13,Four power to deal with it swiftly and
OL,14,Frobustly.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
